<volume>图形系统</volume>
<method>CDateTimePicker::New </method>
    <description>
        <para>
            CDateTimePicker初始化。
        </para>
    </description>
    <syntax>
        <return_val> ECode </return_val>
        <parameters>
            <api_param>
                <param_inout>[in]</param_inout>
                <param_type> WString </param_type>
                <param_name> caption </param_name>
                <param_note>
                    <para>
DateTimePicker 的文字说明                    </para>
                </param_note>
            </api_param>
            <api_param>
                <param_inout>[in]</param_inout>
                <param_type> Int32  </param_type>
                <param_name> style </param_name>
                <param_note>
<para>
DateTimePicker 的风格，详见 <link url="../../datatype/ControlStyle.htm">ControlStyle</link> 和 <link url="../../datatype/DateTimePickerStyle.htm">DateTimePickerStyle</link>。不同风格可以通过“|”（或）配合使用</para>
                </param_note>
            </api_param>
            <api_param>
                <param_inout>[in]</param_inout>
                <param_type> Int32  </param_type>
                <param_name> x </param_name>
                <param_note>
                    <para>
DateTimePicker 的左顶点在其父类控件中的横坐标                   </para>
                </param_note>
            </api_param>
            <api_param>
                <param_inout>[in]</param_inout>
                <param_type> Int32  </param_type>
                <param_name> y </param_name>
                <param_note>
                    <para>
DateTimePicker 的左顶点在其父类控件中的纵坐标                    </para>
                </param_note>
            </api_param>
            <api_param>
                <param_inout>[in]</param_inout>
                <param_type> Int32  </param_type>
                <param_name> width </param_name>
                <param_note>
                    <para>
DateTimePicker 的宽度                    </para>
                </param_note>
            </api_param>
            <api_param>
                <param_inout>[in]</param_inout>
                <param_type> Int32  </param_type>
                <param_name> height </param_name>
                <param_note>
                    <para>
DateTimePicker 的高度                    </para>
                </param_note>
            </api_param>
            <api_param>
                <param_inout>[in]</param_inout>
                <param_type> IControl *  </param_type>
                <param_name> parent </param_name>
                <param_note>
                    <para>
DateTimePicker 的父类控件接口指针                    </para>
                </param_note>
            </api_param>
            <api_param>
                <param_inout>[out]</param_inout>
                <param_type> IDateTimePicker**   </param_type>
                <param_name> datetimepicker </param_name>
                <param_note>
<para>指向 <link url="../../interface/IDateTimePicker.htm">IDateTimePicker</link> 接口指针的指针，用于获取 IDateTimePicker 接口指针</para>
                </param_note>
            </api_param>                                                             
        </parameters>
    </syntax>

<return>
    <table>
	        <th>
	    	    <td>常见返回值 </td>
	    	    <td>描述</td>
	        </th>
	        <tr>
	    	    <td>NOERROR</td>
	    	    <td>方法调用成功</td>
	        </tr>
	        <tr>
	    	    <td>E_INVALID_ARGUMENT</td>
	    	    <td>参数无效</td>
	        </tr>
	        <tr>
	    	    <td>E_OUT_OF_MEMORY</td>
	    	    <td>没有足够的空间</td>
	        </tr>
	    </table>
    <para>其它参见<link url="../../../../../../car_technology/fundamental/development_environment/car/ECode.htm">ECode</link>相关帮助。</para>
</return>
<remarks>
	  <para>
	  	  当创建了一个 DateTimePicker 对象后，就可以获取 <link url="../../interface/IDateTimePicker.htm">IDateTimePicker</link> 接口指针，通过该接口指针，您就可以调用给种方法对该 DateTimePicker 设置各种属性值。
	  </para>
	  <para>
	  	  默认情况下 DateTimePicker 在日期风格下显示，且日期的格式为：year / month / day。当 DateTimePicker 的风格设置为 DateTimePickerStyle_NoArrow 时，用户只能通过键盘设定日期或者时间。显示日期或者时间的格式可以通过调用 <link url="../../interface/IDateTimePicker/SetFormat.htm">SetFormat</link> 方法。DateTimePicker 控件宽高的取值必须配合控件显示内容的长度和高度，否则无法正常显示时间或者日期，故一旦显示出现上述情况，请先修改下宽高值或者调整下字体的大小，有关更多信息请参考：<link url="../../reference/SetText.htm">如何设置控件所显示的文本</link>
	  </para>
	  <para>
	  	  DateTimePicker 在此 <link url="../../datatype/DateTimePickerStyle.htm">DateTimePickerStyle_DateTime</link> 风格下显示，即又显示日期又显示时间，暂未实现。
	  </para>
</remarks>
